    "en": {
      "title": "Negotiations to buy fuel and gas on loan from Qatar",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Minister of Power and Energy Kanchana Wijesekera, who is on an official visit to the State of Qatar, held discussions with the Deputy Director General of the Qatar Fund for Development and discussed obtaining fuel and gas on loan to Sri Lanka.",
        "The Deputy Director General of the Qatar Fund for Development has informed the Minister that funds have been allocated for medical supplies and that the International Monetary Fund's request for credit facilities will be considered."
      ],
